{"id":160986,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/德国之声-通货膨胀率继续上升/","date":"2011-06-14T17:00:17Z","modified":"2017-01-12T04:04:49Z","title":"德国之声 | 通货膨胀率继续上升","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据德国国际通讯社报道，食品价格攀升使中国</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月份通货膨胀率增至</span><span>5.5%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，创下几乎</span><span>3</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年来最高纪录。今年</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月，中国通胀率为</span><span>5.3%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span><span>3</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月份</span><span>5.4%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，为</span><span>32</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月以来的最高。经济专家们曾预期这一通胀率，而政府则预测今年居民消费价格上升指数为</span><span>4%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。根据国家统计局周二（</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>14</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）公布的数字，上个月，食品价格上涨</span><span>11.7%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，主要原因是干旱和其他自然灾害，以及需求增加。为抑制通胀，北京政府从去年</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月以来已连续</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">次上调利率。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15152010%2C00.html&#038;title=%E9%80%9A%E8%B4%A7%E8%86%A8%E8%83%80%E7%8E%87%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"h